fields.name: Zebra Plant
fields.description: The Zebra Plant, known for its distinctive striped foliage, adds a touch of boldness to indoor spaces. Flourishing in indirect Light and moist soil, this plant showcases its unique patterns while bringing a sense of vibrancy and life indoors.
